history.content: Come out to support the Tech+ Social Impact team to meet Technical Program Manager at Google and Harvard alum Gracie Elqura and learn about the innovative ways technology can be used to improve education. From course/curriculum development to learning theory to developing creative technologies for learning, Gracie has done it all. It’s this Thursday, Nov. 29th 5PM-6PM at the Wozniak Lounge (Soda). Free Sliver and drinks provided! RSVP at the new event link: https://www.facebook.com/events/287628651885840/
history.subject: Tech+ Social Impact Talk with Gracie Elqura
